# Carbon Patterns — How to Look Up

This repo **does not embed** IBM's full content; the authoritative source is on the official site.

1. **Human-readable table of contents**: `docs/patterns/carbon-design-system.md`
2. **Link inventory (JSON)**: `src/accord/patterns/carbon-universal-patterns.json`
3. **Overview**: [Carbon — Patterns overview](https://www.carbondesignsystem.com/patterns/overview/)

When implementing, always prioritize satisfying this repo's **`*.spec.json`**, `.cursorrules`, and Business component constraints; Carbon is for **composition and workflow** reference only — component APIs follow DesignAccord.
